<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('./partials/head.ejs', {
    pageTitle: 'About BookLantern',
    pageDescription: 'BookLantern is an open library that brings together the web’s trusted open stacks so you can read in one clean place.'
  }) %>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/site.css">
  <style>
    .about-hero{background: radial-gradient(1000px 420px at 10% -10%, #e9f0ff 0%, transparent 55%), radial-gradient(800px 340px at 95% 0%, #e8fff7 0%, transparent 60%), #f7f9fc; padding: 64px 0 24px;}
    .about-hero .inner{max-width: 880px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center; padding:24px;}
    .about-hero h1{font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 56px); letter-spacing:-.02em; margin:0 0 12px;}
    .about-hero p{max-width:820px; margin:0 auto 16px; color:#556070; font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,20px);}
    .cta-row{display:flex; gap:10px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:12px;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>

  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="inner">
      <h1>About BookLantern</h1>
      <p>
        BookLantern brings together results from <strong>globally trusted libraries</strong> across the web
        so you can discover <strong>millions of free and public-domain books</strong> in one place—then read
        them in a clean, unified reader.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn" href="/read">Browse Books</a>
        <a class="btn alt" href="/watch">Explore Videos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="value-strip">
    <div class="container value-inner">
      <div class="value-item">
        <div class="vi-title">Millions+ titles</div>
        <div class="vi-copy">Search across vast public-domain and free-to-read catalogs.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <div class="vi-title">From globally trusted libraries</div>
        <div class="vi-copy">One search, many sources—kept simple for readers.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <div class="vi-title">One clean reader</div>
        <div class="vi-copy">Distraction-free pagination, bookmarks, and a consistent reading flow.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="shelf-header">
        <h2>Our mission</h2>
        <div class="hint">Access + delight</div>
      </div>
      <p style="max-width:820px; color:#556070; line-height:1.6;">
        BookLantern is an <strong>open library</strong> in the marketplace sense. We don’t try to own every
        book—just as an open marketplace doesn’t own every product. Instead, we <strong>index and organize</strong>
        freely available texts from around the web, so readers don’t have to create ten accounts on ten sites
        or learn ten different interfaces. Create <strong>one account</strong> on BookLantern, search once, and
        <strong>read in one place</strong>.
      </p>
      <p style="max-width:820px; color:#556070; line-height:1.6;">
        We respect availability and always keep you focused on the text. No clutter, no gimmicks—just books.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> BookLantern • Built on open libraries • <a href="/read">Start reading</a>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
